FUNCTION CombineHalfBytes : USINT
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
//  SRCI Robot Library                                                
// ------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
//                                                                           
//  Object:      CombineHalfBytes                                       
//  Author:      Thorsten Brach                                                
//  Date:        2024-06-01
//
//  Description:                                              
//   
//                                                                           
//  Copyright: 
//    (C) 2024 Thorsten Brach. All rights reserved                                                                         
//                                                                           
//  Disclaimer:                                                                           
